    <abstract>
      <t>The AAA Working Group has been defining requirements for Network Access in Inter-Domain (roaming) networks, including requirements from the Mobile IP and NASREQ Working Groups. Some of these requirements were input from work done in the 3rd Generation wireless SDOs. These same SDO's have a need to tie their IP Intelligent Servers (e.g. Softswitches, Call Agents, SIP Servers, etc.) to their AAA infrastructure.</t>
